      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPIRIT OF PEACE (7) flew home from beyond midfield last start to be just 0.5L off the winner. He's inching closer toward another victory and the in-form Atzeni hops back in the saddle. Can go one better this time around. MEOWTH (9) has gone under narrowly his past two over this course and distance and rises up to C3 today. he drops 6.5kg for the rise in grade however and he rates highly on his most recent outings. Can lob into a midfield position and go one better. METRO POWER (5) came to this track and trip for the first time last week and turned in a strong performance from the front. Orman remains in the saddle and this looks to shape very similarly. Can be prominent in the run and will take some catching. LOVE TOGETHER (1) is better than he sowed last start where nothing really went right. Can be better for that run and return to his best form.",
